{"tid":1189220,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人船P, 窮拎勿入。","createTime":"2019-06-06T16:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T08:26:44.000Z","uid":137339,"like":42,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edde195c0fc3d25390bbbeb086f552594bc0d099","tid":1189220,"uid":137339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。朝早出海。 <br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻龍舟 , 租的。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VExJRmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVExJRmk.jpg&h=a1382c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全部都是女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知咩料啦<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙嘅龍舟 坐20人 台灣式龍舟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g86bfPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg86bfPa.jpg&h=a092860a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通龍舟<br />\n搞手會買好多傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期五 朝早7點天星碼頭集合<br />\n男仔／識玩龍舟：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識啲俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返日。"},{"pid":"4aa8998f7d43accb5168e9578df0bd800188c6bf","tid":1189220,"uid":137339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"好似好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdb2836268c0afc5f977771a55cf1b188cfbd38","tid":1189220,"uid":72240,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"屌，隻狗係我張床柯屎"},{"pid":"b24192de7ba00665822be43f38ffdf59a40c1a97","tid":1189220,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":